---
title: Chorizo Burrito Bowl with Avocado Pico de Gallo and Cilantro-Lime Rice
description: Juicy chorizo takes center stage with cilantro-lime rice as its co-star. The addition of a fresh and creamy avocado Pico de Gallo makes a great extra in this soon-to-be award-winning dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-burrito-bowl-7c0f04f4.jpg
